headline: Looking At The Narrative For ONEOK OKE After Shifting Analyst Targets
summary: The blended fair value estimate for ONEOK has been adjusted slightly, shifting from US$88.63 to about US$87.50 per share, as recent Street research has converged around a more balanced, wait and see stance. Behind this, some analysts are trimming expectations while others see enough support in the current setup to keep price targets closer to where the stock already trades. headline: A Look At ONEOK (OKE) Valuation After Dividend Increase And New Independent Directors
